TY  - JOUR
T1  - Unveiling the link between firm ESG performance and CSR disclosure quality: The mediating impact of stakeholder attention
AU  - Shao, Fangjing
AU  - Qin, Chuan
AU  - Wen, Chunran
JO  - International Review of Financial Analysis
